text: Provides wonderful activities for seniors by instructors who are enthusiastic, patient & kind. I'm attending a few: Zumba Gold, Vitality exercises & Qigong. There are other activities: you are free to choose. You also get to go on excursions for such a miniscule amount (usually $2 but balloting is necessary as they are popular). Annual membership is only at a token sum of $12, $1 a month!
Got a cup of coffee here to support! It's actually open to public, so if you'd love to get a cup of coffee do come by! Uncle is really nice.
A nice place for seniors to gather, interact and makan. This place's concept won the Singapore President's Design Award. The staff here are friendly!
